When you perform this operation through any node, the node will disconnect automatically with the current wallet detached from it. It is prescribed in the settings of the node. The cost will be 3 coins.
When this operation is performed, the node is activated by binding the current wallet. It is prescribed in the settings of the node. Any wallet is considered tied to a node if it made a transaction through it, even if it is not spelled out in the node settings. If the balance of this wallet decreases below 100 coins, or if no transactions are created in a node for more than 14 days, or no any wallet is tied to the node for 6 hours after the wallet of the node prescribed in the settings is untied, the node is automatically turned off. The date of the last transaction created is displayed on the node page in the 1 column. The cost of activating a node will be 102 coins.
To access the contact book and receive e-mail notifications of incoming and outgoing transactions (if E-mail notifications are configured on the node), you need to save the existing password on the settings page or create a new password of at least 6 characters here. Node services are accessed with the saved password without the need to perform paid transactions using a private key. When performing any paid transaction through another node, access to the node services is removed and the password must be set again. Saving contacts and setting up E-mail notifications will become available in two of minutes, after a new password is created. If you already have a password, enter it without a private key and click the send button next to the blank private key field. The cost of creating a new password to the node will be 3 coins.

Creating a private key takes up to 10 minutes...

When creating a new referral wallet, you need to fill in the private key field. The referrer field can be left blank. If you write any active wallet in the referrer field, the created wallet will become a referral of this wallet. When specifying in the referrer address G-1, wallet created will have no referrers and it will not be someone's referral. The cost will be 5 coins.The new wallet successfully created and activated in two minutes. Be sure to save its number and its private key, which are above this text. It is impossible to restore a private key! Transactions are performed only when using the private key. If there are no incoming and outgoing transactions on the wallet within 3 days, the wallet is deleted and 3 coins are returned back to the wallet of the node from which the registration was made. Any paid action is an outgoing transaction. Changing the private key too.
The chat message is written in Latin letters and will appear on all nodes two minutes after sending your signed transaction with it. At the same time, the wallet that created the message will be published. Chat number, where the message will appear, consists of 13 digits and is written above in the appropriate form. Chats: 1000000000000 - advertisements (message in it is published from the button in the form of a horn), 1000000000001 - main chat, 1000000000002 - arbitrators for arbitration. You can create your own chat with your number. For example, create a chat number by region code, country code, zip code.
The wallet entry field contains the wallet number to which the message is addressed. You can leave this wallet field blank. For the convenience of copying the wallet into this field, in the chat you need to click on the wallet number of the person who sent the message and its number will be inserted into the filter field. Then, press the button to send the message to the chat and the wallet number from the filter form is inserted into the field of the recipient's wallet. By posting a message in a chat, you agree that mat, insults and other illegal statements are prohibited and that the message is stored distributed on all nodes in the transaction your signed. Therefore, the message will not be moderated. It will be public and accessible to all and only you are responsible for it. The lifetime of the ad is 7 days and then it will be deleted automatically. The cost will be 3 coins, but, in order to protect against spam, there should be at least 1 000 coins on the balance sheet.
